  (10)  READ-ITEM B ; IF END OF DATA GO TO OPERATION 12 .
  (11)  JUMP TO OPERATION 1 .
  (12)  SET OPERATION 9 TO GO TO OPERATION 2 .
  (13)  JUMP TO OPERATION 2 .
  (14)  TEST PRODUCT-NO (B) AGAINST ; IF EQUAL GO TO OPERATION 16 ;
